# Code Owners for the Micro-Learning App
#
# This file defines who should review and approve changes to different parts of the project.
# GitHub will automatically request reviews from these people when PRs touch these files.
#
# For more info: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Frontend team - reviews all frontend changes
/frontend/ @frontend-lead-1 @frontend-lead-2

# Backend team - reviews all backend changes
/backend/ @backend-lead-1 @backend-lead-2

# DevOps/CI-CD team - reviews deployment and infrastructure
/.github/workflows/ @devops-lead-1 @devops-lead-2
/docs/DEPLOYMENT.md @devops-lead-1 @devops-lead-2

# Documentation team - reviews all documentation
/docs/ @docs-lead-1 @docs-lead-2
*.md @docs-lead-1 @docs-lead-2

# Architecture - tech leads review
/docs/ARCHITECTURE.md @tech-lead-1 @tech-lead-2

# Everyone should review API changes
/docs/API.md @tech-lead-1 @tech-lead-2

# Database schema and models
/backend/src/**/models/ @backend-lead-1 @backend-lead-2

# Contributing guidelines
CONTRIBUTING.md @project-manager-1 @project-manager-2
